snippet.textDisplay: A beautiful rendition of sayonee. Unlike the orignal it is the fusion of rock and qawali so they added rahat for the qawali feel and ali noor for the rockish feel. The jugalbandi of electric guitar and violin and then the solo seemed perfect. In the first half i was like what is this , this sounds like the orignal one nothing new. But when Salman with his solos kicked in, i was like ab maza ayega. Kamran Mannu did a splendid job with the bass and one and only ahad niyani was awesome as always. Just loved it.
